00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
<c.chapter>Introduction</c>

2
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
OpenSPP Registry Tutorial - Learn how to register individuals, create groups, and manage beneficiaries

3
00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:05.500
<c.chapter>Part 1: Registering Individuals - Creating new beneficiary records</c>

4
00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:10.236
Navigate to Registry > Search to open the Registry Search Portal

5
00:00:10.236 --> 00:00:14.169
Click "New Individual" to register a new person

6
00:00:14.169 --> 00:00:20.459
Enter the individual details: family name, given name, and other required fields

7
00:00:20.459 --> 00:00:24.589
Click Save to register the individual

8
00:00:24.589 --> 00:00:28.919
Search for the newly created individual to verify registration

9
00:00:28.919 --> 00:00:30.919
<c.chapter>Part 2: Creating Groups - Organizing individuals into households</c>

10
00:00:28.919 --> 00:00:35.344
Click "New Group" to create a household or organization

11
00:00:35.344 --> 00:00:38.054
Opening the group registration form...

12
00:00:38.054 --> 00:00:41.661
Enter the group name and save

13
00:00:41.661 --> 00:00:46.002
Search for the group to verify it was created

14
00:00:46.002 --> 00:00:48.002
<c.chapter>Part 3: Adding Members - Linking individuals to groups</c>

15
00:00:46.002 --> 00:00:51.579
Open the group to add members

16
00:00:51.579 --> 00:00:56.396
Click "Add a line" and search for the individual to add as a member

17
00:00:56.396 --> 00:01:01.360
Save the group with the new member

